* pattern_bt.sno
* Bottleneck: pattern backtracking, alternation, node allocation
* Match attempts requiring backtracking. Expected: 200000
        &ANCHOR = 0
        PAT = ('aaa' | 'bbb' | 'ccc' | 'ddd') SPAN('abcd') . W
        S = 'xxxxxxxxxxbbbccccddddaaaaxxxxxxxxxxbbbccccddddaaaa'
        N = 0
LOOP    S PAT                          :F(DONE)
        N = LT(N, 200000) N + 1        :S(LOOP)
DONE    OUTPUT = N
end
